@startuml seq_25_ban_mute_user
title Sequence Diagram: UC-25 Ban / Mute User

actor Moderator
participant "User Web" as Frontend
participant "Moderation Controller" as Controller
participant "Moderation Service" as Service
participant "Restriction Repo" as Repo
participant "User Repo" as UserRepo

Moderator -> Frontend: (1.1/2.1/3.1/4.1) Select Ban/Mute & Submit details
Frontend -> Controller: (4.2) POST /api/moderation/users/{id}/restrict {type, duration, reason}
Controller -> Service: (5.1) Restrict User
Service -> UserRepo: (5.2) Validate moderator permissions & target user
UserRepo --> Service: (5.3) Validation passed

alt Action is Ban
    Service -> Repo: (6.1) Insert Ban record
    Repo --> Service: (6.2) Ban record created
else Action is Mute
    Service -> Repo: (7.1) Insert Mute record
    Repo --> Service: (7.2) Mute record created
end

Service --> Controller: (8.1) Updated Restriction State
Controller --> Frontend: (8.2) 200 OK
Frontend --> Moderator: (8.3) Show success & update user status UI
@enduml
